body.description: Brilliant Oral Care Program Looking to train your baby with proper oral care but don’t have the proper tools? Brilliant Oral Care guides you and your baby with a step by step program to achieve your goal. Discover the effect you have on your child’s oral care by starting in their early years to help develop a love of brushing and good oral habits throughout. Treat your teething child, to a baby-friendly Wipe-N-Brush. The two-fold solution uses soothing Xylitol tooth wipes with a silicone Wipe-N-Brush fitting on the finger. Giving you scrubbing power to eliminate harmful plaque that sticks to teeth and gums, they promote a healthier mouth while soothing and massaging. Food grade silicone and natural Xylitol wipes make Baby Brilliant’s Wipe-N-Brush a popular choice among parents, taking the 'bite' out of teething. For newborn’s tender gums and baby’s teething, the products are designed to take care of gums and budding baby teeth from an early age with soft and safe products that children love to chew on. Once your child’s teeth erupt, the program progresses to the distinctive Brilliant Toothbrushes. Our Toothbrushes feature all-around bristles for an all-around clean, that easily clean those hard-to-reach places where food and plaque can hide, causing tooth decay. The program continues onto the Brilliant Toothbrushes for adults and specialized oral care, also designed with a unique, patented 360° brush. Brilliant brings you oral care for the significant other as well as the whole family. Give your child the gift of a lifetime by developing good oral care habits with the innovative Brilliant Oral Care Program by Baby Buddy because 'Every Baby Needs a Buddy'.
